          >
            Building <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-400 via-primary-400 to-cyan-400">PSIKOPAT</span> Leaders
          </h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="overflow-hidden">
          <p
            id="hero-subtitle"
            class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-xl opacity-0 translate-y-full leading-relaxed"
          >
            Class 2KS4 â€” where innovation meets collaboration. Together we create, learn, and grow.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div id="hero-cta" class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 opacity-0 translate-y-full">
          <a
            href="/anggota"
            class="group relative px-8 py-4 bg-primary-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-primary-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(14,165,233,0.6)] hover:scale-105"
